==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Intercontinental
<hw>In`ter*con`ti*nen"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Between or among continents; subsisting or carried on between
continents; <as>as, <ex>intercontinental</ex> relations or
commerce</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Passing between continents or capable of passing
between continents; <as>as, an <ex>intercontinental</ex> ballistic
misile; an <ex>intercontinental</ex> airplane flight</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interconvertible</ent>⟦br⟧
